<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p class="updated">Last updated: June 20, 2026</p>

<p>Murottal Juz Amma Offline ("the App") is developed by Bozo ("we", "us"). This privacy policy explains how we handle information when you use the App.</p>

<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
<p>This App <strong>does not collect, store, or share your personal data</strong> on our servers. All core features (audio playback, surah list, favorites, last played history, and settings) run entirely <strong>offline</strong> and are stored only on your device using local storage (DataStore).</p>

<h2>2. Locally Stored Data</h2>
<table>
    <tr><th>Data</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Storage Location</th></tr>
    <tr><td>Favorite surahs</td><td>Display your favorites list</td><td>Local device (DataStore)</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Last played history</td><td>"Continue Listening" feature</td><td>Local device (DataStore)</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Language & theme preference</td><td>Display personalization</td><td>Local device (DataStore)</td></tr>
</table>
<p>This data is never sent to any server and will be automatically deleted if you uninstall the app.</p>

<h2>3. Advertising (Google AdMob)</h2>
<p>This App displays ads using <strong>Google AdMob</strong>. AdMob may collect the following data for ad personalization purposes:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Device identifier (Advertising ID)</li>
    <li>Approximate general location (country/region)</li>
    <li>Technical device information (model, OS version)</li>
</ul>
<p>Ads only appear when you have an internet connection. Data collection and use by AdMob is governed by <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

<h2>4. App Permissions</h2>
<table>
    <tr><th>Permission</th><th>Reason</th></tr>
    <tr><td>Internet</td><td>Loading AdMob ads</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Foreground Service</td><td>Background audio playback</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Notifications</td><td>Display audio playback controls</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>5. Audio Content</h2>
<p>All murottal audio files are bundled within the app since installation (offline). No audio is downloaded or streamed from any server.</p>

<h2>6. Children</h2>
<p>This App is safe for all ages, including children, as there is no inappropriate content and no direct personal data collection from users.</p>

<h2>7. Policy Changes</h2>
<p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page.</p>

<h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
<p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact: <strong>on.bozo@gmail.com</strong></p>
